      "role": "user",
      "content": "okay cool. one more thing, i was reading a random thread online that said mixing antidepressants with herbs can sometimes cause serotonin syndrome which sounds scary... is that actually something i need to worry about? since i'm taking both for a bit, how do i know if i'm okay?",
